<h2 id="5">openrouter_api: An OpenRouter client library</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-5">
<p>
Archive: <a href="https://discuss.ocaml.org/t/ann-openrouter-api-an-openrouter-client-library/18016/1">https://discuss.ocaml.org/t/ann-openrouter-api-an-openrouter-client-library/18016/1</a>
